    "summary": {
      "value": "Use Might for Magic Checks, and treat weapons relying on Might as being arcane."
    },
    "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered one or more Classes among <strong>Chimerist</strong>, <strong>Darkblade</strong>, <strong>Esper</strong>, <strong>Fury</strong>, and <strong>Wayfarer</strong>.</p><hr /><p>When you perform a Magic Check for a spell or Ritual, you may replace <strong>one</strong> of the Attributes with <strong>Might</strong> (such as <strong>【MIG + MIG】</strong> for a Chimerism Ritual).</p><p>As long as the <strong>Accuracy</strong> formula of a weapon you have equipped includes <strong>Might</strong>, you may treat that weapon as also belonging to the <strong>arcane</strong> Category for the purpose of Skills and effects that require it.</p>",
